  <entry>
    <title>recoil状态管理</title>
    <link href="/2023/07/26/recoil%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86/"/>
    <url>/2023/07/26/recoil%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="mobx"><a href="#mobx" class="headerlink" title="mobx"></a>mobx</h2><p><img src="https://p3-juejin.byteimg.com/tos-cn-i-k3u1fbpfcp/bbfd472bb1e2416ea3289ee09e11b917~tplv-k3u1fbpfcp-zoom-in-crop-mark:4536:0:0:0.awebp" alt="image-20201124155837753"></p><ul><li><p>只能通过状态提升至公共祖先来共享状态，但可能导致一颗巨大的树重新渲染。</p></li><li><p>上下文（context）只能存储一个值，而不能存储一组不确定的值，且每个值都有自己的使用者（consumers）。</p></li><li><p>这两种方式都很难将组件树的叶子节点（使用状态的地方）与组件树的顶层（状态必须存在的地方）进行代码分拆。</p></li></ul><h2 id="recoil"><a href="#recoil" class="headerlink" title="recoil"></a>recoil</h2><h4 id="核心概念"><a href="#核心概念" class="headerlink" title="核心概念"></a>核心概念</h4><ul><li><code>Atoms</code> atom 是状态的单位，组件可以订阅、更新这些状态。当一个 atom 发生变化，每个订阅它的组件都会根据最新的状态进行重新渲染。</li><li><code>Selectors</code> selector 是一个纯函数，用于计算基于状态的派生数据。它接收 atoms 或其他 selectors 做为入参，当上游状态发生变化时，selector 将进行重新计算。跟 atom 一样，订阅 selector 的组件也会按新状态进行重新渲染。</li></ul><h3 id="方法"><a href="#方法" class="headerlink" title="方法"></a>方法</h3><ol><li>初始准备</li></ol><p>想要在项目中使用 Recoil 管理状态，第一步就是用 <code>RecoilRoot</code> 将要管理的组件像下面这样包裹起来，什么都不用传递。</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs react">...<br>import &#123; RecoilRoot &#125; from &quot;recoil&quot;;<br><br>function App() &#123;<br>  return (<br>    &lt;RecoilRoot&gt;<br>      &lt;A /&gt;<br>      &lt;B /&gt;<br>    &lt;/RecoilRoot&gt;<br>  );<br>&#125;<br>...<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ol start="2"><li><strong>创建状态</strong>(atom&#x2F;selector)</li></ol><p>如 Filter 组件代码所示，我想要通过 <code>年龄</code> 和 <code>性别</code> 2 个条件去筛选数据。前面提到了在 Recoil 中，atom 是状态的单位，下面为这 2 个条件分别创建一个 atom。</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs php">import &#123;<br>  ...<br>  atom<br>&#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;recoil&quot;</span>;<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">age</span> = <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">atom</span>(&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">key</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;age&quot;</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: undefined,<br>&#125;);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> <span class="hljs-variable constant_">gender</span> = <span class="hljs-title function_ invoke__">atom</span>(&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">key</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender&quot;</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: undefined,<br>&#125;);<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>需要注意的是，创建 atom 时， <code>key</code> 和 <code>default</code> 都是必选的，key 做为 atom 的唯一标识在整个项目中必须是唯一的。default 是你为这个状态设定的默认值，这里我都用了 undefined。</p></blockquote><ol start="3"><li><strong>订阅更新状态</strong>(api)</li></ol><p>状态创建好了，下一步就是如何在组件中订阅、更新该状态了。这里需要用到 Recoil 提供的自定义 hook，先简单介绍 3 个常用的：</p><ul><li><code>useRecoilState</code> 当组件同时需要读写状态时使用</li><li><code>useRecoilValue</code> 当一个组件需要在不写入 state 的情况下读取 state 时使用</li><li><code>useSetRecoilState</code> 当一个组件需要写入而不需要读取 state 时使用</li></ul><p>从使用角度来看，<code>useRecoilState</code> 和 React 自带的 <code>useState</code> 用法完全一样，而<code>useRecoilValue</code> 和 <code>useSetRecoilState</code> 分别是只读和只写两种情况的对应版本。</p><blockquote><p>在 Filter 组件中，要做的只是确认筛选条件，即只需要写入状态：</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> gender = <span class="hljs-title function_">atom</span>(&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">key</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender&quot;</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">default</span>: <span class="hljs-literal">undefined</span>,<br>&#125;);<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Filter</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 这里相当于完成了组件和状态的关联</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> setGender = <span class="hljs-title function_">useSetRecoilState</span>(gender);<br><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<br>    <span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">section</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">            ...</span><br><span class="language-xml">      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">dt</span>&gt;</span>Gender<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">dt</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;radio&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;man&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">onChange</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#123;()</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="language-xml">              setGender(&quot;man&quot;); // 写入新状态</span><br><span class="language-xml">            &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="language-xml">          /&gt;</span><br><span class="language-xml">          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">label</span> <span class="hljs-attr">htmlFor</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;man&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Man<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">input</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">type</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;radio&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">name</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;gender&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">id</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;woman&quot;</span></span></span><br><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-attr">onChange</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#123;()</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="language-xml">              setGender(&quot;woman&quot;); // 写入新状态</span><br><span class="language-xml">            &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="language-xml">          /&gt;</span><br><span class="language-xml">          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">label</span> <span class="hljs-attr">htmlFor</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;woman&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Woman<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">label</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">        <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">dd</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">dl</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">      ...</span><br><span class="language-xml">    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">section</span>&gt;</span></span><br>  );<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成条件写入后，就需要根据当前条件去筛选数据了，前面已经用过了 atom，接下来该轮到 <strong>selector</strong> 登场了。如果在核心概念部分你还没有完全理解什么是<code>计算基于状态的派生数据</code>，那么相信看完下面的代码你应该可以理解了。</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript"><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> &#123;<br>  ...<br>  selector<br>&#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> <span class="hljs-string">&quot;recoil&quot;</span>;<br><br>...<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> list = <span class="hljs-title function_">selector</span>(&#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">key</span>: <span class="hljs-string">&quot;list&quot;</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">get</span>: <span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">&#123; get &#125;</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// atom gender 做为入参</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> genderState = <span class="hljs-title function_">get</span>(gender); <br>    <span class="hljs-comment">// 返回根据 genderState 过滤的结果</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> developers.<span class="hljs-title function_">filter</span>(<span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">item</span>) =&gt;</span> &#123;<br>      <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> genderState ? item.<span class="hljs-property">gender</span> === genderState : <span class="hljs-literal">true</span>;<br>    &#125;);<br>  &#125;,<br>&#125;);<br><br>...<br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">List</span>(<span class="hljs-params"></span>) &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-comment">// 这里订阅了 list selector，每次它因为不同条件发生变化时，List 组件都会响应并重新渲染</span><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">const</span> result = <span class="hljs-title function_">useRecoilValue</span>(list);<br><br>  <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> (<br>    <span class="language-xml"><span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">      ...</span><br><span class="language-xml">      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">        &#123;result.map((item) =&gt; (</span><br><span class="language-xml">          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">tr</span> <span class="hljs-attr">key</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#123;item.id&#125;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span>&#123;item.avatar&#125;<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span>&#123;item.name&#125;<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span>&#123;item.age&#125;<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">            <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span>&#123;item.gender&#125;<span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">          <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">        ))&#125;</span><br><span class="language-xml">      <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">tbody</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="language-xml">    <span class="hljs-tag">&lt;/<span class="hljs-name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br>  );<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>List 组件只响应展示数据，整体结构和接入状态前并为发生什么变化，计算的过程都在 selector 中完成。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>typeScript</title>
    <link href="/2023/07/25/typeScript/"/>
    <url>/2023/07/25/typeScript/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="ts基础"><a href="#ts基础" class="headerlink" title="ts基础"></a>ts基础</h2><p>根目录下添加tsconfig.json</p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs javascript">&#123;<br><span class="hljs-string">&quot;compilerOptions&quot;</span>:&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;watch&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><span class="hljs-comment">//自动调用tsc命令</span><br>        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;removeComments&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><span class="hljs-comment">//删除源文件中注释减小体积</span><br>        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;target&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-string">&quot;es5&quot;</span><span class="hljs-comment">//指定想要编译js版本</span><br>        ......<br>        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;noImplicitAny&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><span class="hljs-comment">//编译器验证更严格,不会自动赋类型any，禁止动态类型</span><br>        <span class="hljs-string">&quot;srtictNullChecks&quot;</span>:<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><span class="hljs-comment">//赋予null/undefined非法</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="限制变量类型"><a href="#限制变量类型" class="headerlink" title="限制变量类型"></a>限制变量类型</h3><figure class="highlight typescript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs typescript"><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">multiply</span>(<span class="hljs-params">a:<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span>,b?:<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span></span>):<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span>&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//没有返回值标记为void</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a*b<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//():返回值类型，默认any，也有number,boolean,string,any</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//? 可选参数</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//对于初值确定的不需要标注</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-attr">point</span>:[<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span>?]<br><span class="hljs-comment">//数组:number[] 二维数组:number[][]</span><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">let</span> <span class="hljs-attr">color</span>:<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span>|<span class="hljs-built_in">string</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//别名</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">type</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">UserID</span>=<span class="hljs-built_in">number</span>|<span class="hljs-built_in">string</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">b</span>(<span class="hljs-params">userid:UserID</span>)&#123;<br>&#125;<br><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">type</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Props</span> = &#123;<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">title</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">string</span><br>  <span class="hljs-attr">onConfirm</span>: <span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">void</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">onCancel</span>: <span class="hljs-function">() =&gt;</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">void</span>,<br>  <span class="hljs-attr">visible</span>: <span class="hljs-built_in">boolean</span><br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">Dialog</span>(<span class="hljs-params">&#123; title, onConfirm, onCancel, visible &#125;: Props</span>) &#123;<br>&#125;<br>    <br><span class="hljs-keyword">function</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">a</span>(<span class="hljs-params">callback:(data:<span class="hljs-built_in">string</span>)=&gt;<span class="hljs-built_in">void</span></span>)&#123;&#125;<br><span class="hljs-comment">//返回值不返回，传参为string类型</span><br><span class="hljs-title function_">a</span>(<span class="hljs-function">(<span class="hljs-params">data</span>)=&gt;</span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-title function_">alert</span>(data);<br>&#125;)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>git指令</title>
    <link href="/2023/07/25/git%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/"/>
    <url>/2023/07/25/git%E6%8C%87%E4%BB%A4/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="git常用"><a href="#git常用" class="headerlink" title="git常用"></a>git常用</h2><p>工作区——&gt;暂存区——&gt;本地仓库——&gt;远程仓库</p><h4 id="初始化"><a href="#初始化" class="headerlink" title="初始化"></a>初始化</h4><p>克隆仓库：git clone &lt;git地址&gt;<br>初始化仓库：git init </p><blockquote><p>新建远程仓库之后可以连接初始化</p></blockquote><h4 id="提交"><a href="#提交" class="headerlink" title="提交"></a>提交</h4><p>添加文件到暂存区：git add -A<br>把暂存区的文件提交到仓库：git commit -m “提交信息”<br>查看提交的历史记录：git log </p><h4 id="回滚"><a href="#回滚" class="headerlink" title="回滚"></a>回滚</h4><ol><li><strong>工作区</strong>回滚：git checkout <filename></li><li>撤销最后一次提交：git reset HEAD^1</li></ol><blockquote><p>单纯修改可以点开history然后手动对比修改</p></blockquote><ol start="3"><li><p>git reset回滚</p><ul><li><p>git log查询版本号<img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20190731102022900.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3l4bHNoaw==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p></li><li><p>（github查询也可以）</p><p><img src="https://imgconvert.csdnimg.cn/aHR0cDovL2ltZy5ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0LzIwMTgwNDE0MjAzMzQ0MTM4" alt="这里写图片描述"></p></li><li><p>使用“git reset –hard 目标版本号”命令将版本回退</p></li><li><p>用git push-f强制推上去</p></li></ul></li></ol><blockquote><p><img src="https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20190731102055301.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3l4bHNoaw==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70" alt="在这里插入图片描述"></p></blockquote><h4 id="分支"><a href="#分支" class="headerlink" title="分支"></a>分支</h4><p>以当前分支为基础新建分支：git checkout -b <branchname><br>列举所有的分支：git branch<br>单纯地切换到某个分支：git checkout <branchname><br>删掉特定的分支：git branch -D <branchname><br>合并分支：git merge <branchname></p><blockquote><p>在哪个分支就是以那个分支为基础执行命令</p></blockquote><h4 id="远程"><a href="#远程" class="headerlink" title="远程"></a>远程</h4><p>推送当前分支最新的提交到远程：git push<br>拉取远程分支最新的提交到本地：git pull</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>hexo相关</title>
